<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></blockquote><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Hi {!Receiving_User.FirstName},</span></font><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br></span><br><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">It's time to get you setup with Alliance Connect.&nbsp;<br></span><br><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Our</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;app gives you access to thousands of shifts, and contracts across Australia. It's where you can let us know when you're available to work, when you've worked and where you can access all your employment related documents and leave details.&nbsp;</span><blockquote style="font-size: 12pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><br></blockquote><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Once you're logged in, <b>r</b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>eview your payroll details</b> or add them if this is your first time logging in.</span><font face="arial"><br></font><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Go to the main menu, open Payroll Profile. Select More, then complete each section:</span><br><ul><li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Payment details</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">TFN declaration</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Superannuation choice</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Deductions (if applicable)</span></li></ul></blockquote><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">To get started, open this email&nbsp;</span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">on your mobile device</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">and follow the link below.</span></blockquote><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><span data-teams="true"><p></p></span></blockquote><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><br></blockquote><blockquote style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><a href="{!Community_Url}">Access Alliance Connect now</a></span></font><br><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br></span></blockquote><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Complete the steps in the setup guide to finalise your Alliance Connect profile.</span><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br></span></blockquote><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Username: {!Receiving_User.Username}</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span><br><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">For more detailed instructions, watch this video:</span><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font><br><a href="https://youtu.be/rSw24bm0YtQ?si=iTVuIZv8XFambGab" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Alliance Connect App demo</a><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span><br><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></blockquote></blockquote><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div><br></div></blockquote><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Kind regards,</span></font></blockquote><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></blockquote><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Alliance Nursing</span></blockquote><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Alliance Rural &amp; Remote Health</span></blockquote><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Alliance Extra Staff</span></blockquote><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br><div style="font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style=""><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style=""><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
